  "3304340": {
    "name": "ELARIENNE",
    "steam_appid": 3304340,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304340/extras/cc4921f11856ee1733da6469fecd7bcd.poster.avif?t=1771081499\" width=640 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304340/extras/cc4921f11856ee1733da6469fecd7bcd.webm?t=1771081499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304340/extras/cc4921f11856ee1733da6469fecd7bcd.mp4?t=1771081499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ELARIENNE：策略决定胜负</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一次召唤就能改变战局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不可预测的变量组成军队，而缜密的策略才是坚持到最后的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有单位召唤都是随机的，从普通阶级到超稀有阶级。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >共8个阶级，以及人类、精灵、兽人三大种族。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个种族都有完全不同的战斗风格，让每次队伍组合都新鲜且无法预料。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想要完成梦想阵容吗？最终能跨越不确定性的，是你的选择与策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在黑暗蔓延的世界里，守护<strong>ELARIENNE</strong>的，唯有你的判断。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304340/extras/d65fceaa66c63e096f6ebeef8a1ccc8f.poster.avif?t=1771081499\" width=600 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304340/extras/d65fceaa66c63e096f6ebeef8a1ccc8f.webm?t=1771081499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304340/extras/d65fceaa66c63e096f6ebeef8a1ccc8f.mp4?t=1771081499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>符文：运气，还是策略？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败史诗首领后，会随机出现 3 个符文供你选择。<br>是再调整一次策略，还是干脆再掷一次骰子——决定权在你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304340/extras/85a5a185849b299ad002b07ab256d028.poster.avif?t=1771081499\" width=540 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304340/extras/85a5a185849b299ad002b07ab256d028.webm?t=1771081499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304340/extras/85a5a185849b299ad002b07ab256d028.mp4?t=1771081499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>150 波生存战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人会一波波出现，沿着固定路径循环前进。<br>清不掉的怪会留在场上，与下一波叠加。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地图上累计到 70 只敌人，或没能在时间限制内击杀首领，这局就结束。<br>当怪物堆到失控，黑暗将吞噬 ELARIENNE，世界随之崩塌。<br>趁还来得及，守住你的防线。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304340/extras/9a74106385fb79ae05e116d7a6a74a61.poster.avif?t=1771081499\" width=640 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304340/extras/9a74106385fb79ae05e116d7a6a74a61.webm?t=1771081499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304340/extras/9a74106385fb79ae05e116d7a6a74a61.mp4?t=1771081499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>随机，但很讲究战术</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一局都不一样。<br>你抽到的单位，会改变之后的符文与升级；<br>而那些选择，会把“随机”变成“策略”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >今天，运气会站在你这边，还是把你推向黑暗？<br>亲自验证一下。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304340/extras/8147762bf095c71961d649072222fff4.poster.avif?t=1771081499\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304340/extras/8147762bf095c71961d649072222fff4.webm?t=1771081499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304340/extras/8147762bf095c71961d649072222fff4.mp4?t=1771081499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
